    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Cerealians are an odd clan. They developed an efficient ocular power to better aid their sniping. However, even with an eye so powerful that it has effects passively, they choose to stay modest. They use their techniques by putting their hands in a sign commonly associated with \"Finger Guns\".</p><h4 id=\"cerealian-traits\">Cerealian Traits</h4><p><strong>Ability Score Increase:</strong> +2 Int, +1 Wis <br /><strong>Speed:</strong> Your base walking speed is 30 feet. <br /><strong>Skill Proficiencies:</strong> Insight, Perception</p>",
